# Directions to L100 Deikhan Cure Trainer (Rico, mob 6766)
say { "Hello";
	say Hello, how are you today?;
	}

say { "trainer";
	tell %n Yes yes, I know where he is but I can only;
	tell %n give you a hint since it's part of your training.;
	tell %n Flock South of Grimhaven then turn east,;
	tell %n Follow the road till you see a north exit.;
	tell %n Read the description's as any good adventurer;
	tell %n must do...If not you won't uncover the clues!;
	cackle;
	}

